quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  19,77,bhala tum ne is shakhs ko dekha jis ne hamari aayton se kufarkiya aur kehnay laga ke ( agar mein az sar e no zindah howa bhi to yahi ) maal aur aulaad mujhe ( wahan ) miley ga
  19,78,kiya is ne ghaib ki khabar palle hai ya khuda ke yahan ( se ) ehad le liya hai ?
  19,79,hargiz nahi. yeh jo kuch kehta hai hum is ko likhte jatay aur is ke liye aahista aahista azaab berhate jatay hain
  19,80,aur jo cheeze yeh batata hai un ke hum waris hon ge aur yeh akela hamaray samnay aeye ga
  19,81,aur un logon ne khuda ke siwa aur mabood bnalye hain taakay woh un ke liye ( mojab izzat o ) madad hon
  19,82,hargiz nahi woh (ma'boodan baatil ) un ki parastish se inkaar karen ge aur un ke dushman (o mukhalif ) hon ge
  19,83,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke hum ne shaitano ko kafiroon par chore rakha hai ke un ko barangekhta karte rehtay hain
  19,84,to tum un par ( azaab ke liye ) jaldi nah karo. aur hum to un ke liye ( din ) shumaar kar rahay hain
  19,85,jis roz hum parhaiz garon ko khuda ke samnay ( bator ) mehman jama karen ge
  19,86,aur gunahgaaron ko dozakh ki taraf pyase haank le jayen ge
  19,87,( to log ) kisi ki sifarish ka ikhtiyar nah rakhen ge magar jis ne khuda se iqraar liya ho
  19,88,aur kehte hain ke khuda beta rakhta hai
  19,89,( aisa kehnay walo yeh to ) tum buri baat ( zabaan par ) laaye ho
  19,90,qareeb hai ke is ( iftira ) se aasman phatt parrin aur zameen shaqq hojaye aur pahar Parah Parah ho kar gir parrin
  19,91,ke unhon ne khuda ke liye beta tajweezkiya
  19,92,aur khuda ko Shayaan nahi ke kisi ko beta banaye
  19,93,tamam shakhs jo asmano aur zameen mein hain sab khuda ke rubaroo bande ho kar ayen ge
  19,94,uss ne un ( sab ) ko ( apne ilm se ) ghair rakha aur ( aik aik ko ) shumaar kar rakha hai
  19,95,aur sab qayamat ke din is ke samnay akailey akailey haazir hon ge
